AR_Viewer should be placed within your C: directory, Utilities 
directory, or within the current working directory.

AR_viewer is used in conjuction with Amiga Report International in
AmigaGuide (r) format.

For those who do not use AmigaGuide (r), may view any pictures
distributed with Amiga Report using AR_Viewer with the following
template:

AR_viewer Filename [xpos] [ypos]



